Help Us Create a More Resourceful World

At Itron, we help our customers make the most of what they have. Our technology connects people, devices and insights to better manage energy and water resources, all around the world. As a global company, we have manufacturing, sales, support and administrative offices in 70 worldwide locations—do you want to help us make a difference?



Explore Current Job Openings



Itron is an Equal Opportunity Employer
Itron will make reasonable accommodation to assist a qualified person with a disability in the job application process.  If you need assistance and would like to request a special accommodation, please contact accessibility@itron.com or at +1-509-924-9900 USA. For more information on Equal Employment Opportunity, please click here.




